snippet.title: Camp Canyonwood - Official Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Camp Canyonwood is coming to Steam Early on August 4, 2022. Watch the latest trailer for another look at this upcoming life sim game, including character creation options, a look at camp life, and more.

In Camp Canyonwood, restore the camp to its former glory. Each summer, teach new groups of campers fun activities like fishing, archery, and stargazing, while protecting them from dangers such as injury, bears, and...aliens.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
